*qdbm-1.8.13 (25 Jul 2004)

  25 Jul 2004; Akinori Hattori <hattya@gentoo.org> +metadata.xml,
  +qdbm-1.8.13.ebuild:
  Initial revision. Based on the ebuild from Atzm Watanabe
  <sitosito@p.chan.ne.jp> in bug #55574, and modified by me.
